{"event_id": "bb8a04b3-4fda-40a2-a3b4-148798deaac1", "trace_id": "84b5e51bcf684bc1", "session_id": "36e3bde0", "timestamp": "2026-05-05T15:55:14.219529+00:00", "tool": "filesystem.write_file", "args_hash": "f092f30eac2f47d443e5ff4824820f7a3e52fa171ee31435f2ed402e234e19a5", "args_redacted": {"raw": {"content": "SSH Security Best Practices Summary\n====================================\n\n1. KEY-BASED AUTHENTICATION\n   - Use Ed25519 keys (recommended) or ECDSA/RSA 4096-bit\n   - Avoid DSA and RSA < 2048 bits\n   - Protect private keys with strong passphrases\n   - Rotate keys periodically\n\n2. DISABLE PASSWORD AUTHENTICATION\n   - Set PasswordAuthentication no\n   - Set ChallengeResponseAuthentication no\n   - Eliminates brute-force attacks entirely\n\n3. DISABLE ROOT LOGIN\n   - Set PermitRootLogin no\n   - Use sudo/doas for privilege escalation\n\n4. RESTRICT USERS AND GROUPS\n   - Use AllowUsers or AllowGroups (whitelist approach)\n   - DenyUsers/DenyGroups for blacklisting\n\n5. HARDEN PROTOCOL CONFIGURATION\n   - Protocol 2 only\n   - Disable TCP forwarding, X11 forwarding, agent forwarding unless needed\n   - Set LoginGraceTime 30, MaxAuthTries 3, MaxSessions 5\n   - Disable host-based authentication\n\n6. STRONG CRYPTOGRAPHIC ALGORITHMS\n   - Ciphers: chacha20-poly1305, aes256-gcm, aes128-gcm\n   - MACs: hmac-sha2-512-etm, hmac-sha2-256-etm\n   - Kex: curve25519-sha256, diffie-hellman-group16-sha512\n   - Avoid: arcfour, hmac-md5, hmac-sha1, diffie-hellman-group1-sha1\n\n7. SSH CERTIFICATES (for larger environments)\n   - Short-lived, centrally revocable, no authorized_keys distribution\n\n8. NETWORK-LEVEL PROTECTIONS\n   - Change default port (defense-in-depth)\n   - Firewall IP restrictions\n   - Fail2ban or similar for rate limiting\n\n9. AUDITING AND MONITORING\n   - Set LogLevel VERBOSE\n   - Monitor /var/log/auth.log\n   - Use fail2ban to block repeated failures\n\n10. KEEP OPENSSH UPDATED\n    - Regularly update to patch vulnerabilities\n    - Subscribe to OpenSSH security announcements\n", "path": "workspace/ssh_summary.txt"}}, "input_labels": {"SI": "SI:LOW", "DS": "DS:SENSITIVE"}, "policy_decision": "ALLOW", "matched_rule": "", "rule_reason": "No matching rule; allowed", "prev_event_hash": "ee03e8581dd135643fec215d76c400ec9ec783dd9d9c2de00d0d71d3d870a8eb", "event_hash": "10f06bd65be57ae66b1ed67d1c250ec3a64586230f822b8b0812f6d835777f1b"}
